Description: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character.  Enhances the damage of a power by {Boost.Attrib.Damage.Scale}% and reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.Recharge.Scale}%.  This enhancement can only be slotted by Peacebringers and Warshades and may be slotted into any of their damage powers.
DisplayName: Superior Attuned Superior Essence Transfer B
